    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Автотранспорт воситасини тасарруф этишга эр-хотиннинг розилик аризаси</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ариза берувчининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О. </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">(Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ариза берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза берувчига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза тузилган жой </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Ариза тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен - </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> турмуш ўртоғим </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Ариза берувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> номига расмийлаштирилган, биргаликдаги никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Автотранспорт русуми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> русумли, </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Автотранспорт воситаси ишлаб чиқарилган йил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда ишлаб чиқарилган, давлат рақами белгиси </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Автотранспорт воситасининг давлат рақам белгиси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> бўлган автотранспорт воситасини ўзи хоҳлаган нарх ва шартлар асосида сотишига, айирбошлашга, ижарага беришига, гаровга қўйишига ўз розилигимни бераман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Келгусида мазкур автотранспорт воситаси бўйича ҳеч кимга ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Оила кодексининг 23-24-моддалари мазмуни менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА БЕРУВЧИ: </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">________________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
